videos.headline: Baylor's drive halted after Trestan Ebner fumbles
videos.description: Baylor RB Trestan Ebner loses the football, and Tyler Lacy recovers it for Oklahoma State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's drive halted after Trestan Ebner fumbles) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor cashes in for score after INT
videos.description: JT Woods gets an interception for Baylor, and then a few plays later, Blake Shapen finds a wide-open Ben Sims for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor cashes in for score after INT) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Drew Estrada makes leaping grab for Baylor TD
videos.description: Baylor QB Blake Shapen lofts the ball into the end zone where a wide-open Drew Estrada makes the catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Drew Estrada makes leaping grab for Baylor TD) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyquan Thornton makes spectacular grab for Baylor TD
videos.description: Baylor QB Blake Shapen drops a dime to Tyquan Thornton, who makes a fantastic catch for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tyquan Thornton makes spectacular grab for Baylor TD) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Jairon McVea dives to pick off Spencer Sanders
videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Spencer Sanders gets picked off for a third time, this time on a diving grab by Baylor's Jairon McVea.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's Jairon McVea dives to pick off Spencer Sanders) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dominic Richardson gives OK State its first TD of the game
videos.description: Oklahoma State RB Domonic Richardson takes the handoff and cruises across the goal line for a score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dominic Richardson gives OK State its first TD of the game) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Spencer Sanders throws his fourth INT of the game
videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Spencer Sanders gets picked off by Baylor for the fourth time in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Spencer Sanders throws his fourth INT of the game) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's muffed punt sets up Oklahoma State with good field position
videos.description: Baylor's Trestan Ebner muffs the punt, and Oklahoma State gets good field position Korie Black recovers it.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's muffed punt sets up Oklahoma State with good field position) 2021/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor denies Oklahoma State on 4th down to win Big 12 title game
videos.description: Baylor's defense comes up big and stops Oklahoma State on fourth down to secure the Big 12 title.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor denies Oklahoma State on 4th down to win Big 12 title game) 2021/12/04 ESHEET
